{"word":"Mary","slug":"mary","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Mary</b> 1. The mother of Jesus:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=16'>Mat 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=38'>Luk 1:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=19'>Luk 2:19</a> <br/> - Visits her cousin Elizabeth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=56'>Luk 1:56</a> <br/> - Attends the feast at Jerusalem with her husband and her son, starts on the return, misses Jesus, seeks and finds Him in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=51'>Luk 2:51</a> <br/> - Is present with Jesus at a marriage in Cana of Galilee<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=10'>Joh 2:10</a> <br/> - Seeks Jesus when He is teaching in a house<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=47'>Mat 12:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=31'>Mar 3:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=19'>Luk 8:19</a> <br/> - Present at the cross<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=27'>Joh 19:27</a> <br/> - Is committed to the care of John<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=27'>Joh 19:27</a> <br/> - Dwells with the disciples in Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=14'>Act 1:14</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=7&verse=14'>Isa 7:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=35'>Luk 2:35</a> <br/> 2. Magdalene:<br/> - Possessed of devils, delivered by Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=9'>Mar 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=3'>Luk 8:3</a> <br/> - Present:<br/> b at the crucifixion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=56'>Mat 27:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=40'>Mar 15:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=25'>Joh 19:25</a><br/> b at the sepulcher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=61'>Mat 27:61</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=28&verse=7'>Mat 28:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=47'>Mar 15:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=7'>Mar 16:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=56'>Luk 23:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=7'>Luk 24:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=1'>Joh 20:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=13'>Joh 20:13</a><br/> - Recognizes Jesus after the resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=28&verse=10'>Mat 28:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=9'>Mar 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=18'>Joh 20:18</a> <br/> 3. Sister of Mary the mother of Jesus, and wife of Cleophas:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=25'>Joh 19:25</a> <br/> - Mother of James and Joses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=56'>Mat 27:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=40'>Mar 15:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=25'>Joh 19:25</a> <br/> - At the sepulcher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=61'>Mat 27:61</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=47'>Mar 15:47</a> <br/> - Assists in preparing the body of Jesus for burial<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=28&verse=1'>Mat 28:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=1'>Mar 16:1</a> <br/> - A witness of the resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=10'>Luk 24:10</a> <br/> 4. Sister of Lazarus:<br/> - Sits at Jesus' feet for instruction<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=42'>Luk 10:42</a> <br/> - Beloved of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=1'>Joh 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=5'>Joh 11:5</a> <br/> - Anoints Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=13'>Mat 26:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=9'>Mar 14:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=2'>Joh 11:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=3'>Joh 12:3</a> <br/> 5. Mother of Mark and sister of Barnabas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=12'>Act 12:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=10'>Col 4:10</a><br/> 6. A Christian woman in Rome<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=16&verse=6'>Rom 16:6</a>"}]}